hostage rescue
40 players
2 random spawned hostages

Another map of my reconstruction project. 
I remade local culture house, where local events and entertainments are taking place. I had real ground plans of building, so except of cellar I made entire building by those plans. After few tests and changes I decided to make roof accessible. It is quite big map, so it lags in some places (explosion in room full of physics stuck game for while).

You can see my own made models in map such as Skoda cars and bus, those models are part of my custom models pack.

If you like this one, check all of my maps here
This map or its parts is also used in my singleplayer mod

Have a fun
Dinus Saurus
